<!--<h4>FIRST FACE.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu 1066 gu nēṁṭi 
<lb n="2"/>māgha bahula 14 maṁggaḷavāramu nā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁḍu bhaṭṭīprōli viṭṭīśvaradēvaraku gaḍivanagō 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kana talli taṁḍrulaku dharmmuvugānu nāṁgarikatumu 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ka Aṁgarikaṁḍu prōlevasamunaṁ beṭṭina A 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kaṁḍadīpamulu reṁḍu dīpamunaṁ ni 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tyamāneṁḍu ne(nē)yi santa(ntā)na kramuṁ 
<lb n="8"/>buna nācaṁdrārkkamu naḍapakalavāru <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

<!--<h4>SECOND FACE.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="9"/>yi dīpamulaku neggu talaṁcinavāḍu 
<lb n="10"/>bāṇarāsi vaccinavāṁḍu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> kavila <note n="212-*">Inscription ends abruptly.</note>
</p>

